law.text: As used in this chapter, "commissioner" shall mean the commissioner of the Department of Workplace Standards, under the direction and supervision of the secretary of the Labor Cabinet.
law.history: Amended 2010 Ky. Acts ch. 24, sec. 1769, effective July 15, 2010. -- Created 1984 Ky. Acts ch. 414, sec. 24, effective July 13, 1984.
